<br>
I've definitely been planning to get the Helm of Ro.  (RP wise it's fun playing a gnome; stat-wise, 83 WIS with items is pretty sad.)  Conveniently enough, I've obtained most of what's required for Ro armor even without consciously working on the quest!  (Had all I need for helm and boots, save for the Sand of Ro -- some of which, I bought off Bakanome as early as yesterday morning. *grins*)<br>
<br>
Crustacean is also something I've been looking at.  Although the stat decreases scare me, most of it's -CHA.  I suppose travelling with an enchantress makes that less of an issue.  And even the -DEX shouldn't be too bad, as it's already fairly high -- around 116 right now, I think.  The trade off would be reaking of fish...<br>
<br>
Ro armor costs about 200pp per piece for the plat bars, and maybe some more since I'll probably want to buy the melatite in the Bazaar (rather than take faction hits), but I could probably afford to throw out my lightcrawler, and replace it with some Ro, and maybe a piece of Crustacean or two.<br>
